</p>\n<p>​\t\t我是这样想的,如果我人有问题,把我辞掉 ,我无话可说 ,但是我天天加班赶进度,领导也没说我进度慢. 我觉得我事做的挺好的.然而老板一句话,觉得项目不重要,就把我给辞了 ,因为在试用期,到时候可能还会被挂一个因为个人原因被辞退 .草了 遇上这种事,还是挺心烦的. 还想的是在新公司里面好好搞点事情出来, 瞬间就没了兴趣.</p>\n<p>​\t\t哎  家人们 ,这样的事情怎么处理啊 .目前项目月底就做完了. 我是忍忍继续搞?还是做完就走啊?前辈们给点意见,谢谢啦. (老板看不见!!!)</p>\n","last_modified":1625535763,"replies":29,"id":787776},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/093f/65e0/59_large.png?m=1615956453","name":"random","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/093f/65e0/59_normal.png?m=1615956453","title":"随想","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/random","topics":2949,"footer":"","header":"有的时候，可以停下来找找灵感，然后再继续。","title_alternative":"Random","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/093f/65e0/59_mini.png?m=1615956453","stars":939,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":59,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"username":"jimmyismagic","website":null,"github":null,"psn":null,"avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a9e9c00252c8378df424490e36db1f4e?s=24&d=retro","bio":null,"url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/jimmyismagic","tagline":null,"twitter":null,"created":1512800185,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a9e9c00252c8378df424490e36db1f4e?s=24&d=retro","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a9e9c00252c8378df424490e36db1f4e?s=24&d=retro","location":null,"btc":null,"id":273408},"last_reply_by":"SurfaceView","last_touched":1625537543,"title":"为什么你越来越不想玩抖音了？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/787774","created":1625535269,"content":"想玩的不用回答\r\n\r\n说说我的感受：好玩的视频越来越少，流量上来了全都是带货的，不纯粹了","content_rendered":"<p>想玩的不用回答</p>\n<p>说说我的感受：好玩的视频越来越少，流量上来了全都是带货的，不纯粹了</p>\n","last_modified":1625537317,"replies":29,"id":787774},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_large.png?m=1615111905","name":"iphone","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_normal.png?m=1615111905","title":"iPhone","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/iphone","topics":8604,"footer":"这里绝不讨论如何获得 iPhone 盗版软件、iTunes 黑卡之类。","header":"Say hello to the future.","title_alternative":